<heading>fg - Bring a job to the foreground.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  fg index
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Brings a suspended or background flow to the foreground
and resumes interactive input for it.

Use the list command to see active flows and their indices.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
bg, stop, list, man
</paragraph>
